{
  "stem": "1918.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was January 21, and in the afternoon, suddenly we heard the oberscharfurer, you know, the top dog, saying, los, los, schnell, schnell immediately!",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to line up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And left the people who were in the revere, they didn't have time to pry them out and put them on stretchers and carry them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They couldn't walk because they had gangrene from digging so deep down that the water came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE] tracks were dug that deep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they left them there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And us, the nearly thousand prisoners, lined up, and immediately we were on our way, marching somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we marched until the night time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where we-- they put us up in a-- an evacuated camp that was evacuated by another thousand prisoners who were continuing the death march.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we woke up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the next day, Monday, we marched again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Monday night, we were housed in an evacuated camp, which was a barn where they held the cows.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And on top where they had the straw, we were housed there, and we buried ourselves in the straw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The four of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The four of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, with typical ingenuity, because who says the Jews are supposed to be so smart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They outsmarted us a thousand times a day, because evil is smarter than good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were evil.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- we hid in the straw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they boiled potatoes outside so that the smell of potato, boiled potato, would lure us out to the marchers, to the people who were already lined up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if we hid anywhere in the straw, they had no time to pick us out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they lured us out with the smell of the potato, and we fell for it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
